<p class="contextTtl" id="p1" data-pid="1"><span id="page131" class="pageNum" aria-hidden="true" data-no="131" data-before-text="131"></span><strong>レッスン32</strong></p>
<h1 id="p2" data-pid="2"><strong>神の王国はもう存在している</strong></h1>
</header>	<div class="clearfix alternatePresentation clickable noTooltips
		">
		<div class="thumbnail">
			<img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1054" class="lightbox"
				 data-alt-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1058"
